AllPrintings.description: Every printing and all cards in each printing.

AllPrintingsCSVFiles.description: Every printing in individual CSV format and all cards in each printing.

AllSetFiles.description: Each individual set file in a directory, compressed.

AllCards.description: Every card as a unique "atomic" object. May also be outputted as every card in a specific set. Some data properties will be omitted if they have differing examples from set to set.

CardTypes.description: Every card type of any type of card.

CompiledList.description: All possible compiled outputs from MTGJSON, such as, AllCards, AllPrintings, Modern, SetList, etc.

DeckLists.description: All possible compiled pre-constructed deck outputs from MTGJSON.

Keywords.description: List of all keywords used on Magic cards.

Legacy.description: All sets, restricted to sets legal in Legacy.

LegacyCards.description: All cards, restricted to cards legal in Legacy.

Modern.description: All sets, restricted to sets legal in Modern.

ModernCards.description: All cards, restricted to cards legal in Modern.

PauperCards.description: All cards, restricted to cards legal in Pauper.

SetList.description: List of codes, names and release dates of all sets.

Standard.description: All sets, restricted to sets legal in Standard.

StandardCards.description: All cards, restricted to cards legal in Standard.

version.description: Metadata object has {{external:ISO-8601$https://www.iso.org/iso-8601-date-and-time-format.html}} dates for latest build and prices, and version properties of this MTGJSON release.

Vintage.description: All sets, restricted to sets legal in Vintage.

VintageCards.description: All cards, restricted to cards legal in Vintage.
